Patch looks good. 

The only edge case I could think of what if the stored value itself is nil.  Here is my solution to handle that case.

```
if fragment = controller.read_fragment(name, options)
   fragment
else
  //check if the key exists
   if controller.fragment_exist?(name)
    // it means stored value is nil
   // return nil otherwise proceed to else
   end
```
